title: Early Week 1 NFL Picks, James Winston suspension talk with John Breech (Football 06/25)
description:
Will Brinson is joined by John Breech to break down the latest news surrounding James Winston and his likely three-week suspension and Odell Beckham possibly still deciding to hold out. Then the guys break down their way-too-early Week 1 NFL picks against the spread.
